    "attributes": {
        "action": "Require secondary schools to have a nine week summer holiday",
        "additional_details": "We as a country need to focus on the well being and rest on kids. We believe students and teachers need more time to rest in the summer in order to full recharge the batteries.",
        "background": "We want the Government to require schools in England to extend the summer holiday in order to give a longer rest to students and teachers. Most schools in Europe get longer breaks and most schools in the US get around two and a half months off.",
